The iron turtle contrloler.

This progect contains:
* source code for processing a program as a server on the Raspberry Pi or other platform,
* source code for processing a video stream from a Raspberry Camera or any other USB camera aproximatly in real time,
* source code for processing hyroboard wheels controller behavior in according to user commands

Here is a lot of compile definitions
* the most important is compiling for Raspberry Pi or for your PC (tested only with Ubuntu)
* other is compiling with different parameters for object detection (actually in this branch, machine vision is disabled, cause it takes a lot of system resource of RPI).

